mily:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">50</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">个；</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">活动产品</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">：【雅妹子】酱肉</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">活动开始时间</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">月2</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"> 20</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">；</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://201106.image.myqcloud.com/201106/0/9d75063a-6c93-4f61-881f-8eace9ffe7fb/original\" width=\"770\" height=\"6040\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '', '1');
