INSERT INTO `cms_article_data` VALUES ('5b30431c2793462fa162cb92a97dde7f', '<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;\">夏天到了，温暖的阳光，<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;\">染红了樱桃，唤醒了桑葚，又到了蓝莓的季节！在V猫庄园500亩的蓝莓园里，一串串如蓝宝石的蓝莓，穿着白色的薄纱倒垂在树枝上。基地负责人李小刚告诉我们，蓝莓的每一穗果都是陆续成熟的，由白色变成紫色需要一个月的时间，真正成熟的蓝莓，花托收缩，表面附着白色果粉，果子呈深紫色。而现在，正是吃蓝莓的好时节。</span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8Z4B6xv0zpabic13ia41WXcVm7B7cc9Zmy27bGazOTVYAkPG98ibibbECyuvtXCD5w0B4B4WGQIYVL3lonF5EaBhYQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.564748201438849\" data-w=\"\" src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/cebf6896-8602-429c-9331-1e2267888ce7/original\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;\" width=\"800\" height=\"451\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<section label=\"Copyright &copy; 2015 playhudong All Rights Reserved.\" donone=\"shifuMouseDownStyle(\'shifu_t_028\')\" style=\"margin:1em auto;padding:0px;max-width:100%;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</div>\r\n<section class=\"\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:auto;border:none;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;word-wrap:break-word=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;margin:0px;padding:5px=\"\" 10px;max-width:100%;border-top-style:solid;border-top-width:2px;border-color:#4676d9;display:inline-block;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;line-height:26.1818px;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:20.3636px;\">100%生态种植 &nbsp;地下水</span>灌溉</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n</section></section>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:20.3636px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">蓝莓原产自北美洲，原是一种野生浆果，学名“越橘”。</span>属于富含花青素很高的蓝色浆果，</span>近几年，蓝莓果因其丰富的营养价值，被世界各国人们追捧，甚至在欧美等国家，蓝莓被誉为“生命果”。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:20.3636px;color:#021EAA;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">蓝莓也号称“黄金水果”，被世界粮食组织评为五大健康水果之首，也是唯一被美国FDA及法国粮油署认定有药用价值的水果。</span></strong></span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">近几年，国内逐渐开始大面积栽种，同时由于蓝莓对于种植的土质要求不高，因此在南北方均有种植。而与北方的的大棚种植不同，<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:20.3636px;color:#021EAA;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">南方以四川、贵州、云南等地均以露天种植方式为主，而露天的种植使得蓝莓不仅在营养价值还是口感上都更甚一筹</strong></span>。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">在位于四川彭州升平镇内的V猫庄园蓝莓基地，基地负责人</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;color:#888888;line-height:23.2727px;\">李小刚</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\">告诉我们，</span><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:20.3636px;color:#021EAA;\">基地内主要种植的是经过嫁接后的野生兔眼与V3、V5的品种，低产量小果型，每年年产量约7~8万斤新鲜蓝莓。</span></strong> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8Z4B6xv0zpabic13ia41WXcVm7B7cc9ZmyD2HGIDTialUo0wSRVpOtjmmWf2AkExOXTS6VT0RNmHQEnkFHpLXe9sw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8435251798561151\" data-w=\"\" src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/4aa56f9b-2eee-4471-961b-5c43ca636ea8/original\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;\" width=\"889\" height=\"750\" /><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n（基地实拍图）</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">说到自家的蓝莓，基地负责人</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;color:#888888;line-height:23.2727px;\">李小刚介绍</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\">，虽然蓝莓树对土壤要求不高，但唯一的条件是必须是在酸性土壤中栽种，因此，在栽种的前3~4个月，必须使用硫磺粉进行土质改良”为它创造一个适合它成长的家是第一步“。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8Z4B6xv0zpabic13ia41WXcVm7B7cc9ZmyqT4tJGIJXLvZPuoDv6wYib1qMdZQgPPkhy7GCqbfxyhNSAxXBg50gow/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.5539568345323741\" data-w=\"\" src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/a34a94eb-e190-41b3-84ae-19a7197ea641/original\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;\" width=\"900\" height=\"499\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#021EAA;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">秋后，是栽种蓝莓的最佳时期，这时候也需要进行施肥，为了保证100%纯天然，李大哥言语笃定的告诉我们栽种至今从未使用任何农药，仅使用机肥，“就是我们普通人家都会用的油枯，这也最好的肥料。”因此，我们基地的蓝莓，只要成熟后可以从树上摘下来直接食用。</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">在有机肥和纯净地下水的滋养下，来年3月，蓝莓树开始发芽。4月中下旬开花，大约10—20天后，蓝莓花凋谢坐果，5月中旬便开启了这趟关于舌尖的健康美味之旅。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<section label=\"Copyright &copy; 2015 playhudong All Rights Reserved.\" donone=\"shifuMouseDownStyle(\'shifu_t_028\')\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:auto;border:none;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;word-wrap:break-word=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"line-height:26.1818px;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:18px;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\">&nbsp;科学化管理 &nbsp;用线网防止小鸟啄伤果子</span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" white-space:normal;widows:auto;line-height:23.2727px;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;word-wrap:break-word=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;color:#888888;\">彭州属于四川盆地亚热带湿润气候区，<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:23.2727px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">气候温和，雨量充沛，四季分明。因此，在气候环境上非常适宜蓝莓的生长。不过，在享受充足阳光的同时蓝莓也是喜水植物。</span></span> \r\n	</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" white-space:normal;widows:auto;line-height:23.2727px;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;word-wrap:break-word=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" white-space:normal;widows:auto;line-height:23.2727px;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;word-wrap:break-word=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:23.2727px;\">据</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:23.2727px;font-size:14px;color:#888888;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:23.2727px;\">李小刚</span>介绍，</span><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:23.2727px;font-size:14px;color:#888888;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:23.2727px;color:#021EAA;\">基地的蓝莓都是按照国家无公害绿色食品操作规则和要求，无论是剪枝、疏花、疏果、浇水等环节都需要进行科学化管理。</span></strong><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:23.2727px;font-size:14px;color:#888888;\">“水肥的比例，每平方浇水都需要准确的计算，过水过肥不但不会促进生长反而会导致树苗死亡。”</span> \r\n	</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong style=\"color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:23.2727px;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:23.2727px;color:#021EAA;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8Z4B6xv0zpabic13ia41WXcVm7B7cc9ZmyWVjlY9ibeNB3DrHEVOEibW8HYLYYCBtmPlKavOl1S6z6LVCdrBiclO9VA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"\" src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/d1f15f10-d651-4f90-aada-b7b3323431c9/original\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;\" width=\"1632\" height=\"1224\" /></span></strong> \r\n		</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0