ortant;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;color:#888888;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">经常食用蓝莓具有保护视力、缓解疲劳、抗辐射、抗氧化、美容养颜、提高免疫力、改善睡眠质量、预防心脑血管、降低胆固醇和预防便秘等多种保健功效，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:23.2727px;color:#888888;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">堪称“世界水果之王”，因此，也是老少皆宜的水果。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;widows:auto;text-align:center;line-height:23.2727px;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n		</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;widows:auto;text-align:center;line-height:23.2727px;box-sizing:border-box=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img data-src=\"http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/wyice8kFQhf5geQK3gu2FUugjB8iaSGpjOiaELyUkOxkYcTC6WqiaValAg/0\" data-ratio=\"0.0017985611510791368\" data-w=\"\" width=\"556px\" _width=\"556px\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"margin:0px auto;padding:0px;height:1.61151079136691px !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;display:block;width:896px !important;visibility:visible !important;\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n<section class=\"\" data-id=\"85446\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-wrap:break-word=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><section style=\"margin:2px 1em;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;border:0px #0C8918;border-image-source:initial;border-image-slice:initial;border-i