;\">果树；</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;text-align:left;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\">2、一对一素材：长期驻扎在庄园的专属服务团队还将定期免费提供基地素材运营团队定期整理庄园作物生长、管理、采摘、领导/客人视察等资料，让庄园主在社交平台上分享大量自己独有的销售素材，解决传统微商粗暴刷屏的弊病，提高成交率；</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;text-align:left;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\">3、V猫庄园<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;line-height:1.6;\">物流专属标签50张</span></strong>。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;text-align:left;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;background-color:#FF2941;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n		<span style=\"text-align:center;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\