INSERT INTO `cms_article_data` VALUES ('780cab82a6d44842a399837f94ffc58e', '<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">每到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">月，车厘子（大樱桃）都会成为最火爆的微商单品：全人群、复购率高、利润丰厚……大量微商都在寻找优质靠谱的车厘子货源。<img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/2c84c8cf-71ea-4c04-b3e6-107dc6725340/original\" width=\"1024\" height=\"636\" alt=\"\" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;color:#E53333;\"><strong>壹|Frist</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\"><strong>——生长环境 得天独厚——</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">公里岷江大峡谷地理位置优越、全年平均日照</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">1800</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">小时、早晚温差巨大、平均海拔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">1500</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;\">米……<span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><strong>这里是全国唯一可以媲美世界知名车厘子产区美国和加拿大的阿坝州汶川县</strong></span>。<img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/7e27f726-1924-4276-8840-265ab88c66b3/original\" width=\"960\" height=\"637\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:宋体;color:#888888;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/df7b87d7-364c-4b7a-a3ad-28448cfa56c8/original\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/3eaa5f1f-3a54-4bff-bf1b-1cd88be75fab/original\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#E53333;\">贰|Second</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>——独特口感 产量有限——</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	每年这里产出的车厘子总是供不应求，每到采摘季80公里都汶高速都会被堵成停车场<span style=\"line-height:22.4px;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/02e603e9-3178-4e57-9597-0300027f2c18/original\" width=\"690\" height=\"460\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;color:#888888;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">由于品质、口感以及独特的汶川情结等因素，让</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#000000;\">汶川甜樱桃（车厘子）</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">在市场上总是供不应求，这也成为了每年</span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">月微商们对此趋之若鹜。</span><strong style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;text-align:center;font-family:宋体;\">但真正的汶川产区车厘子，资源却十分有限，四川省外的网商</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;text-align:center;\">/</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;text-align:center;font-family:宋体;\">微商更是难求正品货源。</span></span></strong><strong style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;white-space:normal;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:宋体;\">事实上，汶川县每年</span>600<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:宋体;\">万斤有限产量的<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:22px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">汶川甜樱桃（车厘子）</span>，仅游客就会从产地买走一大半。</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;font-family:宋体;\">但据不完全统计，每年市场上却能卖出将达到</span><span