r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">—— 政府聘请 ——</span><br />\r\n</span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;white-space:normal;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">为了让全国更多消费者能够品尝到真正原产地的汶川甜樱桃（车厘子），</span><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;font-family:宋体;\">今年汶川政府公开聘请</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;\">2</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;font-family:宋体;\">万名“</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;\">2016</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;font-family:宋体;\">正品汶川甜樱桃（车厘子）网络推广大使”</span></span></strong><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;white-space:normal;color:#888888;font-family:宋体;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">，<span style=\"color:#000000;\">成功申请获聘的微商，将收到政府发放的</span><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.6;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">“网络推广大使”</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\">聘书实物，同时可以通过</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;white-space:normal;color:#000000;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">V</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;white-space:normal;color:#888888;font-family:宋体;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">猫庄园在汶川雁门乡原产地获得自己的</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.6;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">“挂牌果园”</strong></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span></span></span></span><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/244a7648-2a49-42ff-aafc-19e262fdaba7/original\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;background-color:#FFFFFF;\" /><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/eddb58a9-3316-4394-8626-1193d1c744cd/original\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;background-color:#FFFFFF;\" /><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">有了聘书和挂牌果园信任背书的微商，销售难度大大降低，同时也能真正代理销售正品汶川甜樱桃（车厘子）。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>——<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">溯源庄园标签</span>——</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#888888;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:22.4px;color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">今年的正品汶川车厘子网络推广大使，除了聘书和挂牌果园，还可以获得专属的庄园标签，消费者会通过庄园标签收到该微商的问候，以及产品溯源证明。</span><strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:14px;\">因此，微商今年做汶川车厘子，不是政府授权的网络推广大使，在汶川没有自己的挂牌果园，消费者收不到专属的庄园溯源标签，那很有可能就是假冒李鬼了。</span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:22.4px;color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:22.4px;color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/79d43a68-205e-4958-8bc2-951520b1f7bb/original\" width=\"744\" height=\"357\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#888888;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/e0889492-4f53-41b0-9a49-0a0cef6a00d4/original\" width=\"720\" height=\"914\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/28719b4f-9208-46b5-975d-3b5754008f50/original\" width=\"900\" height=\"723\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#888888;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:22.4px;color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">——</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">如何申请</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">——</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#888888;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#888888;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:22.4px;color:#000