INSERT INTO `cms_article_data` VALUES ('9803f2396bbc44a196a96f1376d6a200', '<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">传承中国文化的不仅仅是唐诗宋词京剧昆曲，更是我们生活中的每一个细节，茶文化亦是如此。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;color:#333333;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">茶，起源于中国。汉族饮茶已有几千年的历史，从作药用到皇家御用，至唐、宋时代，茶已成为“人家一日不可无”的普遍饮用之品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;color:#888888;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;color:#333333;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">中国俗语中的开门七件事“柴米油盐酱醋茶”亦表明了茶在中国文化中的重要性，同时茶也深受文人雅士的喜爱，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">与“琴棋书画诗酒”并列。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/a0e270f7-cb18-4265-a680-c6d98a32c347/original\" width=\"900\" height=\"522\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:normal;widows:auto;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">在秦以前，产茶和饮茶主要流行于四川一带，明代顾炎武的《日知录》写到：秦人取蜀，始知若饮事”。可见，饮茶风习是从四川传出来的。而这其中，作为“蜀中之冠”的雅茶迄今已有2000多年历史。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;white-space:normal;widows:auto;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/6daab6a5-d242-4462-afc8-c1748667f7f4/original\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" alt=\"\" /></span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;widows:auto;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;font-family:微软雅黑, 宋体;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">春暖时节，草长莺飞，又到了一年采春茶的季节。久等了一冬的茶农们都在此时翘首期盼，等着尝鲜。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;widows:auto;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, 宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">对于喝茶的人来说，春茶自然是好的，尤其是头道春茶，经过了一个冬天的休眠和养分储备，让其在春天的第一片芽叶中累积爆发，个中充满了鲜灵之气，仿佛将整个天春天都藏到了那一口翠绿茶汤中，令人神清气爽，心旷神怡。</span><span style=\"color:#333333;\"></span><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/d517e222-8d2f-43be-bd82-7cf808252ef5/original\" width=\"1723\" height=\"1060\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22.3999996185303px;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\">采摘头道春茶，也就意味着老吴的炒茶坊开始忙碌起来。炒茶师傅老吴，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:22.4px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#333333;\">和朋友合伙开了一个专门制茶工作坊，老吴靠手艺吃饭，自然成为了茶叶的制作人。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22.3999996185303px;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\">从弱冠之年的阳刚少年到而今四十不惑，经他翻炒过的茶叶以万计数。老吴说，炒茶多年，自己最擅长的是头道春茶碧螺春的</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:22.3906px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#333333;\">炒制</span><span style=\"color:#333333;\">手艺。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/a065a295-e8cb-4cae-a6fb-e60a0b505843/original\" width=\"1770\" height=\"1147\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:22.4px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">为了保证口感，早上10点之前茶农们就必须把新鲜采摘的茶叶送到老吴这里，过称、查看茶叶成色、筛选、去掉黄叶，散叶之后，老吴就开始茶叶的制作。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22.3999996185303px;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;widows:auto;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span st