INSERT INTO `cms_article_data` VALUES ('9bd0f908be3545d5a5eac756609def32', '<section class=\"\" data-id=\"85446\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-wrap:break-word=\"\" !important;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\">攀枝花，对于从来没有去过的我来说，对它的了解不过是别人口中的天气很好，湛蓝的天空，灿烂却不太耀眼的阳光，仅此而已。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">而第一次真正感受到攀枝花的阳光，是在品尝了家在攀枝花的朋友</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;color:#888888;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">父母寄过来的芒果，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">一个个金灿灿的果子整齐排列，虽还未打开包装但一股芒果的清香已经扑鼻而来。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> <span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">细腻的果肉、丰沛的果汁、纯甜的口感，让人感觉身虽未到达，但心已然至此。原来，这就是人们嘴里常说的代表攀枝花的阳光味道。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;color:#888888;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8Z4B6xv0zpZibmInIHNSWjpXsx9KBBmC8ib2GVMACAnHC7UHhN6Os1KOccfgk6ecJ7WUXPqeTSFoG3V0icfdMbrHQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"\" src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/b792e122-7ef4-4dca-904e-d0fb2c7571b6/original\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" /><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;color:#888888;\">6月的成都</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\">，天气已经算得上是好了。但是，当V猫农特产先锋团一行驾车进入攀枝花境内的时候，对比起来，成都的天气已然是到了相形见绌的地步了。</span> <span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"> </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\">行驶在路上，抬头看见的是满眼湛蓝，朵朵白云为天空添多一抹自然色彩。灿烂的阳光打在脸上，让我们因赶路产生的疲惫感随之消失。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\">据了解，攀枝花在2011年时种植面积已达17万亩，因此芒果园随处可见，似乎连空气都散发着一丝丝芒果的香甜。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8Z4B6xv0zpZibmInIHNSWjpXsx9KBBmC8FCVKqNU84J52G3AdVwopYmaOloPCnc7mib0gcdMAzibDN0FA6o4GcuLQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"\" src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/d99ab16c-921e-47dc-b697-6018a2d005a9/original\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;\" width=\"1045\" height=\"784\" /><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#FF4C00;font-size:14px;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:20.3636px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">【基地实拍】</strong></span> <span style=\"margi