00\" height=\"1300\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"NewStyle15\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"NewStyle15\" style=\"margin-left:18.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\">5、消费者的交易流程？</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	点击“立即购买”——&gt;选择数量——&gt;\"确认支付\"——&gt;选择支付方式——&gt;支付成功\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://201106.image.myqcloud.com/201106/0/5bce3919-d3d1-4a42-b59f-1d64231ca89a/original\" width=\"3280\" height=\"1940\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://201106.image.myqcloud.com/201106/0/ca6a2fae-de81-4762-bc7f-5e84b61760bb/original\" width=\"3280\" height=\"1940\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\">6、消费者支付安全吗？</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;\">V猫平台的交易均属于担保交易，在买家确认收货之后，V猫店主才能获得支付款。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\">7、消费者的订单谁来发货？</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;\">订单全部由供应商发货，不包邮的产品由消费者承担邮费。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\">8、V猫店主如何追踪物流进度？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14.44444465637207px;line-height:23.33333396911621px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\"><strong>点击“小店打理”——&gt;</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\">\"订单管理\"——&gt;“查看物流”</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\"><img src=\"http://201106.image.myqcloud.com/201106/0/70de9fb5-a07b-46e8-8025-98b340126749/original\" width=\"4370\" height=\"1940\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\">9、消费者在哪里查看物流进度？</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;\">通过朋友分享给你的产品链接进入消费者客户端，查看流程如下：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://201106.image.myqcloud.com/201106/0/99facd0f-ca92-4be5-91ec-02bfacbdaa56/original\" width=\"5460\" height=\"1940\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://201106.image.myqcloud.com/201106/0/87b1a497-5bd2-4a87-99ad-ec6119c364b4/original\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '', '1');
