x;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;\">————————</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">在这里，</span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">昼夜温差大，降雨稀少，光照充足</strong></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">，</span><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;\">才得以成就了</span></strong><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;\">口感脆甜、色泽迷人</span></strong><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;\">的</span></strong><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;\">汶川大樱桃</span></strong><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">，也叫做车厘子或甜樱桃。</span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:1em;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.6;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;\">汶川县雁门乡，这个被誉为“云朵上的街市”的羌族村寨种植了大量的大樱桃</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">，驶离213国道往村子的10公里山路，两旁有多得让你惊叹的樱桃林，关键是这里也是了解羌族建筑、文化的好地方。</span><span style=\"font-size:1em;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/976d964a-6f19-4b77-83f2-47bc06aae036/original\" width=\"900\" height=\"598\" alt=\"\" /> </span><span style=\"font-size:1em;line-height:1.5;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:1em;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">在雁门乡麦地村，<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">汶川大樱桃（车厘子）种植园地处于<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">无污染的岷江<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">上游的干旱河谷地带，海拔1500—2000米。</span></span></span></strong></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">这里常年天空湛蓝、阳光明媚、气候干燥，岷江河穿境而过，水量丰富。优越的地理条件让生长在<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">这里的大樱桃果实红艳、果子细腻且脆甜，含铁量居水果之首。</span></strong></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/7bea522a-44b2-4a03-8d58-2e4e24097a39/original\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" style=\"text-align:left;white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.5;\" /><span style=\"text-align:left;white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;text-align:right;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"line-height:1.5;white-space:pre-wrap;text-align:center;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:50px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">2、</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"line-height:22px;color:#888888;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">独特口感</span></span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"line-height:1.5;white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;\">————————————</span></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">2005年，<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">村民陈幺哥成为了村里最早种植汶川<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">大樱桃（车厘子）</span>的农户，</span>前后加起来一共10多亩地。果园的所有<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">果树树龄均在10年以上</span></strong>，与其他小树龄果园里的果实相比，<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">单果在10克左右（约一元硬币大小），所产出的果实更加香甜</span></strong>。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">陈幺哥说，</span>和国外车厘子的绵密口感相比，<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">汶川<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">大樱桃</span></span></strong><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">（车厘子）</span>更具特色，在</span><strong style=\"line-height:1.5;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;\">口感上脆嫩多汁，甜美中一丝果酸味</span></strong><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">，丰富了果肉的层次，从而提升了口感。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/c3151ff0-06e8-497a-abb8-fef951946230/original\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" /><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;color:#888888;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">在离家大约1公里处的山坡上，陈幺哥的<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\">汶川大樱桃（车厘子）</span></span>园里，朵朵花蕾在接受春雨的洗礼后，慢慢的伸展开身姿，娇艳欲滴的樱花在大地的映衬下更加洁白无瑕。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/929aeae1-9fa5-404b-a000-dfd5ccae3ea9/original\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1280\" alt=\"\" /></span><strong style=\"line-height:1.5;text-align:right;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:50px;line-height:22px;\"><strong style=\"line-height:1.5;text-align:center;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">3、</span></span></strong><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">舌尖上的享受</span></span></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"line-height:1.5;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;\">————————————</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;color:#888888;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">三月樱花烂漫，四月翠绿色的小青果子开始挂上枝头，等到<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">五月的时候，红彤彤的<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">汶川大樱桃（车厘子）</span>就正式上市销售了</span>。</span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:4em;font-size:14px;color:#888888;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">陈幺哥告诉我们，<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;line-height:22px;\">汶川大樱桃</span></strong><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:22px;\">（车厘子）生育期短，</span></span><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#FF2941;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;\">从开花至果实成熟仅50~60天左右，拥有绝佳的品质与口味，供应时间为5月到6月份，如果还想品尝美味则需再等一年</span></strong><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/c2d7cebe-7fbf-4e84-8f22-5f5a012c4d83/original\" width=\"719\" height=\"539\" alt=\"\" style=\"line-height:1.5;white-space:pre-wrap;\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">值得一提的是，陈幺哥告诉我们，汶川所