r:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">国内专家研究表明，<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#FF2941;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">汶川<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">大樱桃（车厘子）</span>品质居全国第一，并获得农业部”绿色食品”称号和农产品地理标志保护。</span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">汶川<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">大樱桃（车厘子）</span>，堪称“水果中的钻石”</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">这也成为了V猫小店农特产体验先锋团把<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">汶川大樱桃（车厘子）</span>基地选在这里的最好理由。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/9bb2aec9-1e9d-410d-983f-413b612cd087/original\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">见识过了汶川<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">大樱桃（车厘子）</span>后，陈幺哥带着我们往山下走去。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\">一群热情好客羌族朋友和一桌美味的特色农家美食为我们的行程画上了圆满的句号。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"> </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/a7ecc3fb-9062-4977-9fc0-49c0bdf16121/original\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" alt=\"\" /></span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;color:#888888;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">V猫小店农特产寻宝先锋团与汶川县雁门乡麦地村石书记等领导，共同探讨关于汶川大樱桃的互联网之路。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/03da41b6-353b-401c-b905-d60969553f1a/original\" width=\"2448\" height=\"2448\" alt=\"\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" /><span style=\"text-align:center;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;color:#888888;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">粮食酒浸泡的桑葚酒，香气四溢。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;text-align:center;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"text-align:center;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"http://image.v-cat.cn/201106/0/19178bd0-be72-4096-a438-7cc7a1e989fb/original\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" /> </span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;color:#888888;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">凉拌的核桃须，你吃过吗？这些才是地道的特色美食，还有萝卜干、浸酸菜、香肠腊肉，最好吃的还是右下方的肥而不腻，入口化渣的熏制五花肉！</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#888888;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">————————————————</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"shifubrush\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#888888;font-size:18px;\